cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper deals with visual sentiment classification, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves learning a unified sentiment latent space, which is achieved through adversarial learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the experiments are conducted on benchmark datasets, which are commonly used in multimedia research (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
